::DeathScythe/Ramulus::

With the help of his jets, DeathScythe slowly gained on SnowCat. His 
shoulders were getting bloodied up from the branches, but he wasn't paying 
attention to them. He roars, getting closer to SnowCat.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus stops as he hears a roar, coming from somewhere in front of him. 
Checking his scanners quickly, he gallops off after DeathScythe.
